description:
Shaman is free for a limited time, and on sale as well! We're also releasing a Unique Execution for that Hero.

About For Honor:
Carve a path of destruction through the battlefield fighting for guts, glory, and survival in For Honor. Enter the chaos of a raging war as a Hero from some of the greatest warrior legacies ever known. For Honor is a fast-paced and immersive experience, mixing skill with visceral, never-before-seen melee combat.

Enjoy incredible seasonal content, engaging campaign and thrilling multiplayer with friends online, in split screen two-player co-op, or solo against AI.

author: Ubisoft
description:
Two worlds collide! Rainbow Six Siege x Ghost in the Shell. Gear up Azami and Lion with Major Motoko Kusanagi and Batou inspired bundles. Available now in-game or at https://rainbow6.com/ingameitems

About Rainbow Six Siege:
Rainbow Six Siege is an exciting, new approach to the first-person shooter experience that puts tactical combat and masterful destruction at the center of the action. Lead your team of unique operators through tense and thrilling combat scenarios, and achieve victory through smart preparation and strategic improvisation. Rainbow Six Siege is available now on Xbox, PlayStation® and PC.

#Ubisoft #R6Siege
